[h1]储存网络[/h1]
[h1][i]Storage Network[/i][/h1]

为《缺氧》添加一个集中式管理窗口，用来查看储存、调度材料、管理生产订单，并接入部分建筑与喷泉输出。

[i]Storage Network adds a compact management panel for storage, production requests, building status, and geyser output in Oxygen Not Included.[/i]

[img]https://i.imgur.com/0dvP5c4.gif[/img]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/w6xAHZD.gif[/img]

[h2]功能[/h2]
[h2][i]Features[/i][/h2]
[list]
[*] 储存总览：分类、总量、容量和周期增减趋势。
[*] [i]Storage overview with categories, item totals, capacity, and cycle trend.[/i]

[*] 支持接入储物箱、部分生产建筑和喷泉。
[*] [i]Enroll storage lockers, supported production buildings, and geysers into the network.[/i]

[*] 拖动物品条目即可在已接入储存之间转移物品。
[*] [i]Transfer items between enrolled storage buildings by dragging item rows.[/i]

[*] 生产建筑可从网络请求材料，并将成品存入匹配储存。
[*] [i]Production buildings can request materials from the network and store finished products back into matching storage.[/i]

[*] 复制人建造可从储存网络调拨材料。
[*] [i]Duplicant construction can use materials from the network.[/i]

[*] 订单中心支持查看当前、全部、运行中、已完成和异常订单。
[*] [i]Order center shows current, all, running, completed, and abnormal orders.[/i]

[*] 窗口支持拖动、缩放和位置记忆。
[*] [i]Draggable, resizable windows with saved positions.[/i]
[/list]

[h2]使用方式[/h2]
[h2][i]How to Use[/i][/h2]
[list]
[*] 从管理菜单打开“储存网络”窗口。
[*] [i]Open the Storage Network panel from the management menu.[/i]

[*] 选中支持的建筑，通过侧屏或用户菜单接入/移出网络。
[*] [i]Select a supported building and use its side screen/user menu to join or leave the network.[/i]

[*] 在窗口中浏览物品、转移储存、配置建筑并查看生产订单。
[*] [i]Use the panel to browse items, transfer storage, configure buildings, and track production orders.[/i]
[/list]

[h2]说明[/h2]
[h2][i]Notes[/i][/h2]
[list]
[*] 本模组是管理与转移工具，不会创建实体物流网络。
[*] [i]This mod is a management and transfer tool, not a physical conveyor network.[/i]

[*] 建筑需要手动接入后才会出现在网络中。
[*] [i]Buildings must be manually enrolled before they appear in the network.[/i]
[/list]

